# ==========================
**/Proposal/
**/Pricing*/
**/vendor/
**/*Pricing*.xlsx
**/*Pricing*.md
**/*Proposal*.pdf
**/*Proposal*.xlsx
**/*Quotation*.xlsx
**/*Quotation*.pdf

# Test fixture exception: synthetic 29-byte placeholder, not a real spreadsheet.
# The sensitive-source fixture must ship this file so CI checkouts can prove
# SENSITIVE-001 fires on user-owned source without blocking release (PI-001).
!tests/fixtures/valid-source-others-and-sensitive/source/Quotation.xlsx

